data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!!! This charming, LIKE NEW, home is ready for your family to settle in and enjoy the holidays. Everything has been updated. With single level living, this home is Perfect for the young and old alike with something for everyone to enjoy. Starting with the inviting front porch, you will love all that this fully remodeled ranch home in fantastic neighborhood has to offer. Enter in through a large foyer with closet, This open concept home lives large and spacious for the square footage. It is light and bright in every room. This home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, eat-in kitchen with pantry and dining area, and a spacious family room with cathedral ceilings and a newly remodeled gas fireplace. The  large laundry room is conveniently located next to the master suite. The master suite boast a large walk-in closet and a beautifully remodeled on suite bathroom with new vanity, light fixtures, modern tile and new tub and toilet. A newly resurfaced deck offers a wonderful place to relax and enjoy family time/ grilling/ entertaining in a private setting. The house has been completely renovated: New paint, New LVP flooring throughout entire house, new updated light Fixtures, New Hardware on all doors and cabinets, Master Bath completely remodeled. Spacious 2 car garage with overhead storage. This all one level home makes for great convenient easy living.  Plumb Creek Park featuring a sweet playground and walking trails is less than a mile away.  Cedar Bluff and Hardin Valley Schools and only minutes to Turkey Creek.  Home is ready for a new family. All you need to do is move in and enjoy!
